          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md text-center">
            <div class="text-orange-600 text-4xl mb-4" aria-hidden="true">üìä</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Performance Reports</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Generate formatted reports for reviews with customizable date ranges and export to PDF or Markdown.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md text-center">
            <div class="text-teal-600 text-4xl mb-4" aria-hidden="true">üë•</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Flexible Relationships</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Track 1:1s with managers, mentors, peers, stakeholders, or create custom relationship types.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md text-center">
            <div class="text-indigo-600 text-4xl mb-4" aria-hidden="true">üîÑ</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">IC & Manager Modes</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Switch between tracking meetings with your manager or managing your direct reports seamlessly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md text-center">
            <div class="text-red-600 text-4xl mb-4" aria-hidden="true">‚åö</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Apple Watch App</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">View meetings, complete action items, and log sentiment directly from your wrist.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md text-center">
            <div class="text-pink-600 text-4xl mb-4" aria-hidden="true">ü§ñ</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">AI Suggestions</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Smart agenda suggestions based on meeting history powered by iOS 18+ on-device intelligence.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md text-center">
            <div class="text-teal-600 text-4xl mb-4" aria-hidden="true">‚ôø</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Accessibility Focused</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Designed with VoiceOver support, Dynamic Type, and high contrast options for inclusive experience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

