              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2" aria-hidden="true">‚úì</span>
                <span>Data export/import (JSON/CSV)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2" aria-hidden="true">‚úì</span>
                <span>Demo mode for exploration</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
